1246404225.title: Musk backs down on SpaceX threat
creator: Associated Press
1246404225.description: As President Donald Trump and Elon Musk argued on social media Thursday, the world’s richest man threatened to decommission a space capsule used to take astronauts and supplies to the International Space Station.
